title: Introducing Kei Kobayashi
description: Kei Kobayashi is the little typhoon. He blows in and schools you. He stands a mighty 4'6" and weighs less than a hundred pounds but has the heart of a Lion. Keep your eye out for him in the NSSA's. AKA "The Karate Kid." The up and coming amateur from San Clemente puts in more hours at Trestles than anyone.
